  <h3 class="subsection-heading">6.2.2 Checking Whether an Action Server is Available (If Server is Operational)</h3>
  <p><code class="param-name ph-generic-inline"">[check_period]</code> is the amount of time (in seconds) at which the node checks whether the action server is available. This returns either <code class="ph-var-inline">True</code> or <code class="ph-var-inline">False</code>.</p>

